ha.com/symbol/VCISY\" title=\"Vinci SA\">OTCPK:VCISY</a>). I firmly believe this business to be a very undervalued, underappreciated, and upside-heavy sort of business - and with a dividend yield. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742259-vinci-stock-this-french-company-still-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:19:40"}, {"id": "4742268", "title": "In Sickness And In Wealth: A Closer Look At Executive Pay In Healthcare", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stack of coins from low to high,tiny men on top\" data-id=\"571606663\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Paper Boat Creative</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Bob Herr and Ryan Oden</em></p> <p>Our research suggests that healthcare firms with sound pay practices may yield healthier returns.</p> <p>In recent years, the global healthcare sector has seen rapid growth and generally strong performance. But its pay</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742268-in-sickness-and-in-wealth-a-closer-look-at-executive-pay-in-healthcare", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:15:00"}, {"id": "4742257", "title": "AT&T's Meteoric Upside Isn't Over Yet", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smart phone with AT&amp;T.com site in the pocket\" data-id=\"458421651\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4256px\" height=\"2819px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">franckreporter</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>2024 has been a great year for shareholders of telecommunications conglomerate <strong>AT&amp;T</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/T\" title=\"AT&amp;T Inc.\">T</a></span>). Year to date, the stock is up 41.5%. And that doesn't even factor in returns from the distributions the business pays out. Since I </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742257-att-meteoric-upside-isnt-over-yet", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:05:39"}, {"id": "4742265", "title": "10 Questions For China In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Multi exposure of virtual abstract financial graph interface on Chinese flag and sunset sky background, financial and trading concept\" data-id=\"1322520591\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4500px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Igor Kutyaev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/lynn-song/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lynn Song</a></em></p> <h2>1 - What growth target will China set for 2025?</h2> <p>China's annual exercise of setting its growth target at the Two Sessions is extremely important as it sets the tone for government policy for the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742265-10-questions-china-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4742256", "title": "Why I'm Downranking Patterson-UTI To Hold", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone captures a breathtaking sunset over the Permian Basin, showcasing an oil rig drilling and fracking for oil, amidst the vastness of the landscape\" data-id=\"1485934644\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">grandriver</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>After two acquisitions last year, (primarily NexTier in a 55% PTEN/45% NexTier combination, as well as technology company Ulterra), oilfield services company Patterson-UTI (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PTEN\" title=\"Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc.\">PTEN</a></span>) bit the valuation bullet in 3Q24: it took write-downs of nearly $1 billion, reducing its accounting</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742256-downranking-patterson-uti-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 11:42:41"}, {"id": "4742254", "title": "JEPQ: Dissecting Its 10% Yield", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Percentage sign\" data-id=\"1692418614\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I am not a big fan of investments that promise high yields or returns. Almost always, there is a compromise in terms of risk or a fundamental weakness. I have explored some of these weaknesses in other covered-call ETFs I recently</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742254-jepq-dissecting-its-10-percent-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 11:11:00"}, {"id": "4742251", "title": "Salesforce: Defiantly An AI Play And Mr. Market Agrees", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536p